{"tid":1963663,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"上原亞衣憂心AV界　橋本有菜呻冇工開","createTime":"2020-04-08T09:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T14:07:50.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2295be07338ebdb485b8c3ab58b8d1fbceba56af","tid":1963663,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:45:38.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎打擊各行各業，AV業界更首當其衝，由於每次拍片都有不少緊密身體接觸，恐防會散播病毒，令不少AV拍攝叫停。人氣AV女優橋本有菜，日前便Twitter大呻疫情影響，令工作大減。<br />\n<br />\n引退後轉行做網紅的前AV女優上原亞衣，近日亦在Twitter留言，對業界表示關心：「很擔心現在還拍AV的女優們，因為拍攝有很多親密接觸，又要在密室中聚集。」而上原防疫意識十分高，每次外出都戴上口罩及手套，又隨身携帶消毒手液等。<br />\n<br />\n日本AV影音網站《FANZA》推出10日圓(約0.7港元)欣賞AV作品的優惠，希望粉絲可以安坐家中，減少外出。"},{"pid":"9dea84c9d2e26dc16bb27c8158794706b6e24c02","tid":1963663,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200408/photo/bkn-20200408115926720-0408_00862_001_02b.jpg?20200408164316\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200408%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200408115926720-0408_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20200408164316&h=a8dfd70c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橋本有菜大呻冇工開。"},{"pid":"f02933ea60df4d98671e3ab732e914568797dd60","tid":1963663,"uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200408/photo/bkn-20200408115926720-0408_00862_001_04b.jpg?20200408164316\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200408%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200408115926720-0408_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20200408164316&h=18e2855c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上原亞衣做足防疫，戴埋口罩手套外出。"},{"pid":"7eaf80d0defdef2a76dadcbdf1725f0ac2a6ecbd","tid":1963663,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T09:46:56.000Z","msg":"私約囉"},{"pid":"c6bab49520fc40b6c720d957bbdbe11bf9bf504b","tid":1963663,"uid":301989,"like":10,"dislike":2,